    new Glasses( '9092, 9093 and 9095', 'flips', 'These will fit over glasses smaller than 132mm, or 5-1/8". The higher the shade number, the darker the lens, which makes for less visibility. The higher the shade number, the more UV and IR protection. The 940 didymium glasses (which are further up the page) will fit inside these glasses, along with other types. Unfortunately the inexpensive 9301\'s do not fit in this frame.', '9092-welding-shade-2-lampwork-glassblowing-safety-glasses-sm.jpg', 'select', null, [['IR Shade 2','18'],['IR Shade 3','18'],['IR Shade 5','18'],], ['10474fcd5bcb76df64e686e99d831c30', '90a43f6b880ba839ae14ce24e6a19229', '1e09e558aeb0221d7f69fc9c5b989128', ], [1,-1,1,]),
